works.description: Dear Google, you had helped us in the past and need your assistance again. There is someone using my  images. You will see that at the 18second mark of my youtube video that they have taken/frozen my image and are using it take you to counterfeit Chinese websites. Note that on my website I have my youtube video embedded. When you do a search on google images for "gear ring" it shows up and shows up on regular search. If needed please email again. Please remove this from image search and regular search.
